description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gatinho purrs with a rating of 94, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 94, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 8 for East, 5 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50941-98592-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [94 Votes, Hall of Fame]
